description: This operation returns a list of the ARNs of the canaries that are associated with the specified group.

parameters.name: GroupIdentifier
parameters.description: Specifies the group to return information for. You can specify the group name, the ARN, or the group ID as the GroupIdentifier.

nested_items.name: Resources
nested_items.description: An array of ARNs. These ARNs are for the canaries that are associated with the group.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates that there is more data available. You can use this token in a subsequent ListGroupResources operation to retrieve the next set of results.
